Solving the ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS error A kind of ERR_TOO_MANY_REDIRECTS error is when we try to acces the wp-admin page.
After trying to change the site address using the popular internet solution, add a couple of line into the wp-config.php file:
/** WP Home Address **/ define('WP_HOME','http://example.com'); define('WP_SITEURL','http://example.com');  Those lines of code do not work correctly and the solution is to change the address fields directly from database. Follow the steps:

